@{PAR}@{FG HIGHLIGHT}@{B}Cut@{UB}@{FG TEXT}@{LINE}
@{PAR}@{B}Cut multiple rectangles out of a portable anymap.@{UB}@{LINE}
@{PAR}Reads a portable anymap as input. Extracts the specified rectangles,
and produces portable anymaps as output.@{LINE}
